Africa Israel Acquires Stake in Negev Ceramics, Calcalist Says

-- B y   R o n i t   G o o d m a n
-- 
2011-03-15T10:55:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/africa-israel-acquires-stake-in-negev-ceramics-calcalist-says.html
Africa  Israel  Industries Ltd.
agreed to buy today Menorah Mivtachim Holding Ltd.’s 6.5 percent
stake in  Negev Ceramics Ltd. (NGEV) , the daily Calcalist said, without
saying where it got the information.  Africa Israel’s offer valued Negev Ceramics at about 300
million shekel, higher than a November offer that valued the
company at 241 million shekels, the newspaper said.   To contact the reporter on this story:
Gwen Ackerman at 
 gackerman@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
